name: Around Football: This City Will Be The Champion!
description:
This banner was found through out Jakarta back in 2018. Jakarta’s Football Club, Persija, was the winner of Indonesian League (Liga 1 Indonesia) in 2018. Thousand of this banner were made by Jakmania, Persija’s supporters before the final game of the season and hang them in all of Jakarta.

Kota Ini Mau Juara = This City Will Be The Champion
----------
Size: 3166 x 2147 px (7,7MB)  
Res: 72px/inch  
Yashica 109 MP, 50mm, Fuji Superia X-Tra 400
  Loc: Jakarta
